maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/161/.orig: Hey girl, ya looking for some rare weapons?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/161/.text: Hé, meuf, tu cherches des armes rares ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/161/.orig: Really? This is a once in a life time offer, ma girl!
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/161/.text: Vraiment ? C'est une offre unique que je te fais, meuf !

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Just a simple trader looking for a particular \c[3]Drill\c[0]...
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Suis juste un simple marchand qui cherche une \c[3]Foreuse\c[0] particulière...
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.note: item 90 or in the same family

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Well look at you, young one.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Eh bien, regardez-vous un peu, jeune femme.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Found yourself something rare with that \c[3]\v[item.90.name]\c[0].
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Avez trouvé quelque chose de rare avec cette \c[3]\v[item.90.name]\c[0].

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Could upgrade it for you if you want...
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Pourrais vous l'améliorer, si vous le voulez...

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Only need certain items for it.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Besoin juste de quelques objets pour ça.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Been a while since I held this in my hands.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Fait un moment que je n'ai pas tenu ce truc dans mes mains.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Time to go. Find a new place to stay.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Il est temps de partir. De trouver un nouvel endroit où rester.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.orig: Maybe we will meet again, can still sense a greater power in my drill.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/215/.text: Peut-être que nous nous rencontrerons à nouveau. Je sens encore que ma foreuse possède encore plus de puissance.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/230/.orig: The \c[3]Don\c[0] might have let you in, but that doesn't mean I have to sell you anything, \v[lore.title.seeker].
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/230/.text: Le \c[3]Don\c[0] vous a peut-être laissé entrer, mais ça ne veut pas dire que je dois vous vendre quoi que ce soit, \v[lore.title.seeker].

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/457/.orig: A seeker inside here? You sure must have some good connections.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/457/.text: Une \v[lore.title.seeker] ici ? Vous devez avoir de bonnes relations.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.orig: This is a private party \c[3]Seeker\c[0], you better run off\..\..\.. fast.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.text: C'est une fête privée, \c[3]\v[lore.title.seeker]\c[0] ! Vous feriez mieux de partir\..\..\.. et vite.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.orig: Unless you got yourself a pass of course.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.text: Sauf si naturellement vous avez un passe.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.orig: What's this? A pass? From the Boss himself?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.text: Qu'est-ce que c'est ? Un passe ? Du boss en personne ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.orig: I don't know what you did \c[3]Seeker\c[0], but rules are rules.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/590/.text: Je ne sais pas ce que vous avez fait, \c[3]\v[lore.title.seeker]\c[0], mais les règles sont les règles.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.orig: Sorry \c[3]Seeker\c[0], the market is closed off for your kinda folks.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.text: Désolé, \c[3]\v[lore.title.seeker]\c[0], le marché est fermé pour des gens comme vous.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.orig: Unless you got yourself a pass, of course.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.text: Sauf si vous avez un passe, bien entendu.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.orig: Now look at that. You got yourself a Pass. From the man himself.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.text: Oh regardez un peu ça. Vous avez obtenu un Passe. Du chef en personne.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.orig: Make sure to leave lots of cash, alright?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.text: Faites en sorte de laisser plein de cash, capich ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.orig: Have fun, \c[3]Seeker\c[0], and don't lose the pass.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/593/.text: Amusez-vous bien, \c[3]\v[lore.title.seeker]\c[0], et ne paumez pas le Passe.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/621/.orig: The rain will cleanse your soul.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/621/.text: La pluie va laver votre âme.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.orig: What's up with this part of town?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.text: C'est quoi le truc avec cette partie de la ville ?
Elle est toute sale et tout.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.orig: Well, apparently this used to be the workers' quarters back when the power plant was built.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.text: Bon, apparemment c'était autrefois le quartier des travailleurs lorsque la centrale électrique a été construite.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.orig: But it became a slum after most of the traders and the general businesses moved in.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.text: Mais c'est devenu la zone, après que les marchands et les entreprises s'y soient installées.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.orig: Wow, alright. Kinda makes you sad, don't ya think?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/624/.text: Wow, OK. Ça rend un peu triste tout ça, tu trouves pas ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.orig: Don't you think it's strange that we don't take damage from the rain?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.text: Tu ne trouves pas cela étrange que l'on prenne pas de dégâts de la pluie ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.orig: I think it's strange that you're sitting on the wet floor.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.text: Je trouve ça étrange que tu t'assoies sur le sol mouillé.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.orig: But yes, it is weird. It's pouring down and I feel the rain, but no damage.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.text: Mais oui, c'est étrange. Il pleut des cordes et je sens la pluie, mais pas de dégâts.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.orig: I guess it's some kind of game development magic again.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/629/.text: J'imagine qu'il y a encore de la magie de développeur de jeu derrière tout ça.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: A Seeker? Should I ask her? Guess she's as good as anyone, really.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Une \v[lore.title.seeker] ? Est-ce qu'il faut que je lui demande ? J'imagine qu'elle est probablement comme les autres.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Hey, ya looking to make some quick cash?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Hé, est-ce que tu veux te faire de l'argent facile ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: My Dad wants me to collect some goods for him from the infested jungle region.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Mon Papa veut que je collecte quelques biens pour lui de la région infestée de la jungle.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: But I ain't no fighter or collector. Dunno why he thinks this is a good "entry trial" too.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Mais j'suis pas un combattant ou un récolteur. J'sais pas pourquoi il pense que c'est un bon "test d'entrée" pour moi.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: So, ya in or out? Ain't got all day.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Donc, t'es avec moi ou pas ? J'ai pas toute la journée.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Good, then let's get down to business.
I need ya to get me 10 \c[3]Venom Shrooms\c[0] and 5 \c[3]Glowing Spheres\c[0], gotcha?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: J'ai besoin que tu me rapportes 10 \c[3]Champis Venins\c[0] et 5 \c[3]Sphères Brillantes\c[0], capiche ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Good, good. Come back when ya got them. And make it quick, ya hear?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Bien, bien. Reviens me voir quand tu les auras. Et fait ça vite, OK ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Buzz off then, I'll find someone to do the work for me.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Casse-toi alors. Je trouverai quelqu'un d'autre pour faire le travail pour moi.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Still here? Doesn't look like ya got my goods. Go on then, make it quick.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Toujours là ? On dirait pas que t'as trouvé mes bousins. Donc pars, grouille-toi !

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Oh it's you. Ya finally got my goods?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Oh, c'est toi. T'as mes bousins ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.orig: Well, about time I might say, woman.
Alright, that's all I need. Here's your cash. Nice knowing ya, I guess.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/632/.text: Bon, c'est tout ce que dont j'avais besoin. Voilà ton cash. Ravi de vous avoir connu, j'imagine.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/633/.orig: Can't do this for dad. Ain't no fighting in me...
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/633/.text: Je ne peux pas faire ça pour papa. Je ne suis pas un bagarreur...

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Sonya Bolt
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Sonya Foudre

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Hi.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Salut.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: A \v[lore.title.seeker], huh!\. I see, an agent of the \v[lore.title.human-government].
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Un \v[lore.title.seeker], hmm ?\. Je vois, un agent des \v[lore.title.human-government].
Salut... ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Yes, the \v[lore.title.human-government], supreme government of all of humanity on \v[lore.title.planet].
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Oui, les \v[lore.title.human-government], le suprême gouvernement de toute l'humanité sur \v[lore.title.planet].

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: The driving force behind exploration of the \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients] and protector of prosperity.\. Among other things.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: La force de frappe derrière l'exploration du \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients] et protecteur de la prospérité.\. Entre autres.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Why...?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Pourquoi... ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Prosperity requires progress and security.\. Power is the key to both.\. And power is gained through tools.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: La prospérité nécessite le progrès et la sécurité.\. Le pouvoir est la clef des deux.\. Et le pouvoir s'obtient à travers des outils.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Tools powered by the Track.\. Tools like you, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. And weapons.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Des outils alimentés par le Tracé.\. Des outils comme vous, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Et des armes.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: How?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Comment ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Seems like there is a solid mind of its own there.\. Want to help me reveal more of the truth?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: On dirait qu'en vous sommeille un esprit bien indépendant.\. Voulez-vous m'aider à révéler la vérité ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Yes, good.\. Motivation worthy of the true \v[lore.title.seeker] spirit.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Bien.\. Je vois que ta motivation est digne du véritable esprit de \v[lore.title.seeker].

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Lea?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Lea ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: The \v[lore.title.seeker]s mission to beat the \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients] for the advancement of shad- and humankind.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: La mission des \v[lore.title.seeker]s est de battre le \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients] pour l'avancement des shads et de l'humanité.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Many have been made puppets of individual interests.\. Corporations, the government, their own personal motives...
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Plusieurs sont devenus des marionnettes d'intérêt privés.\. Les entreprises, le gouvernement, leurs propres motivations personnelles...

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: ... why?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: ... pourquoi ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Greed, \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients].\. Thirst for power and control.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: L'avarice, le \v[lore.title.track-of-ancients].\. La soif du pouvoir et du contrôle.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: And the population turns a blind eye, as long as peace in their little worlds is maintained.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Et la population ferme les yeux, tant que la paix dans leurs petits mondes est maintenue.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: We can make a difference here, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Bring the results of those actions to light.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Nous pouvons changer cela, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. De mettre au grand jour ces actions.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: How?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Comment ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Let's not waste too many words.\. Time is already short.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Ne perdons pas trop de mots.\. Le temps est déjà compté.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Go to \c[3]Clinging River in \v[area.jungle.name]\c[0] and search for suspect lifeforms.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Allez à la \c[3]Rivière Stagnante dans le \v[area.jungle.name]\c[0] et cherchez des formes de vies suspectes.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: I will keep contact with the \v[lore.title.direct-link] and give you further instructions.\. Good luck, \v[lore.title.seeker].
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Je vais garder le contact via \v[lore.title.direct-link] et vous donner plus d'instructions.\. Bonne chance, \v[lore.title.seeker].

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Bye.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Bye.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: [shakes head]
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Maybe I was wrong.\. If you prefer to be blind, be blind.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Peut-être que j'ai eu tort.\. Si vous préférez être aveugle, alors restez aveugle.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: ...bye?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: ... bye ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Sonya Bolt
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Sonya Foudre

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Go to \c[3]Clinging River in \v[area.jungle.name]\c[0] and search of suspect lifeforms.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Allez à la \c[3]Rivière Stagnante dans le \v[area.jungle.name]\c[0] et cherchez des formes de vies suspectes.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: I will keep contact with the \v[lore.title.direct-link] and give you further instructions.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Je vais garder le contact via \v[lore.title.direct-link] et vous donner plus d'instructions.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Sonya Bolt
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Sonya Foudre

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Hi.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Salut.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: \v[lore.title.seeker], you returned!\. I am impressed.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: \v[lore.title.seeker], vous êtes revenue !\. Je suis impressionnée.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Why?
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Pourquoi ?

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Assassinations.\. Bribery.\. After all you have learned, these methods would have been possible.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Des meurtres.\. De la corruption.\. Après tout ce que vous avez appris, ces méthodes auraient pu être une conséquence logique.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Sorry, for not telling you beforehand.\. This mission was too important for you to refuse.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Désolé de ne pas vous l'avoir dit avant.\. Cette mission était trop importante pour que vous la refusiez.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: It all turned out well, \v[lore.title.seeker], so calm down.\. You may be too valuable to them.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Tout s'est bien passé au final, \v[lore.title.seeker], donc calmez-vous.\. Vous semblez trop importante à leurs yeux.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: This time, however, you were truly valuable to humanity.\. These documents will be of great use in fighting injustice.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Cette fois, par contre, vous avez été d'une grande importance pour l'humanité.\. Ces documents seront d'une grande utilité pour mettre fin à cette injustice.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Well then... here are your rewards.\.\. And also my farewell.\. Stay vigilant.
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Et sinon... voici votre récompense.\.\. Et mes adieux.\. Restez vigilant.

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.orig: Sonya Bolt
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/682/.text: Sonya Foudre

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.orig: ... Human want trade?\. Valuable trade.\. Precious egg!
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.text: ... Humain veut marchander ?\. Bon marché.\. Œuf Précieux !

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.orig: ... Trade.\. Trade good.\. Enjoy good egg!
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.text: ... Marché.\. Bon marché.\. Bonne chance avec œuf !

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.orig: Me leave.\. More business.\. Not follow!
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.text: Moi partir.\. Plus d'affaires.\. Pas suivre !

maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.orig:
The \c[3]\v[g.birdScam] \v[item.623.name]s\c[0] turned out to just be \c[3]\v[item.503.name]\c[0]!

\c[1]It was a scam!\c[0]
maps/jungle-city/east.json/entities/687/.text:
Le \c[3]\v[g.birdScam] \v[item.623.name]s\c[0] était en fait juste une \c[3]\v[item.503.name]\c[0] !

\c[1]C'était une arnaque !\c[0]
